{"title":"Install certain python version in Linux","uid":"83fc4bf0106b2e566bb88fa07ace1ff9","slug":"Deploy/Linux/install certain python version in Linux","date":"2023-10-25T17:22:23.000Z","updated":"2023-10-27T18:39:57.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Deploy/Linux/install certain python version in Linux.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JBR-Bunjie/JBR-Bunjie/main/back.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Install-certain-python-version-in-Linux\"><a href=\"#Install-certain-python-version-in-Linux\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install certain python version in Linux\"></a>Install certain python version in Linux</h1><h2 id=\"1-for-Ubuntu\"><a href=\"#1-for-Ubuntu\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"-1: for Ubuntu:\"></a>-1: for Ubuntu:</h2><p>just: apt install python3.8</p>\n<h2 id=\"Zero-try-to-download-python3-8-through-yum\"><a href=\"#Zero-try-to-download-python3-8-through-yum\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Zero, try to download python3.8 through yum\"></a>Zero, try to download python3.8 through yum</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum list | grep python3</code></pre>\n\n<p>find no python38, so choose to setup python3.8 through make install</p>\n<h2 id=\"First-download-the-python-file\"><a href=\"#First-download-the-python-file\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"First, download the python file\"></a>First, download the python file</h2><p>go to website: <a href=\"https://www.python.org/ftp/python\">https://www.python.org/ftp/python</a> to choose correct file</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>example: <a href=\"https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.8.10/Python-3.8.10.tgz\">https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.8.10/Python-3.8.10.tgz</a></p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.python.org&#x2F;ftp&#x2F;python&#x2F;3.8.10&#x2F;Python-3.8.10.tgz</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"unzip-make-and-install\"><a href=\"#unzip-make-and-install\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"unzip, make and install\"></a>unzip, make and install</h2><ol>\n<li>在编译前先在&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local 建一个文件夹 python3（作为 python 的安装路径，以免覆盖老的版本）</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkdir &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>解压：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tar -zxvf Python-3.8.10.tgz</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>进行指定目录的编译安装</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">.&#x2F;configure --prefix&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3 # 设置编译安装路径\n\nmake # 编译\n\nmake install # 安装</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>创建软链接</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ln -s &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3  &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3.8\n\n# 修改旧版本软连接：ln -s &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3  &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;pythonv</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"检验安装\"><a href=\"#检验安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检验安装\"></a>检验安装</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">python3.8 -V\n# Python 3.8.10</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/leon-zyl/p/8422699.html\">centOS 下升级 python 版本，详细步骤 - leon-zyl - 博客园 (cnblogs.com)</a></p>\n","text":"Install certain python version in Linux-1: for Ubuntu:just: apt install python3.8 Zero, try to download python3.8 through yumyum list | grep...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":5,"path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":10,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Install-certain-python-version-in-Linux\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Install certain python version in Linux</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-fo